      refine Or.inr ‚ü®Sum.inr ‚Åª¬π' s, ?_, ?_‚ü©
      ¬∑ exact hs.preimage_of_isOpenMap Sum.inr_injective isOpenMap_inr h
      ¬∑ exact (image_preimage_eq_of_subset h).symm
  ¬∑ rintro (‚ü®t, ht, rfl‚ü© | ‚ü®t, ht, rfl‚ü©)
