theorem isPreconnected_iff_subset_of_disjoint_closed :
    IsPreconnected s ‚Üî
      ‚àÄ u v, IsClosed u ‚Üí IsClosed v ‚Üí s ‚äÜ u ‚à™ v ‚Üí s ‚à© (u ‚à© v) = ‚àÖ ‚Üí s ‚äÜ u ‚à® s ‚äÜ v := by
